dct_title_s: Princeton Quadrangle, New Jersey, 7.5 minute series (topographic)
dct_description_sm: United States. Geological Survey. 7.5-minute series (topographic) U.S. Geological Survey Relief shown by contours and spot heights. Alternate title: Princeton, NJ. In upper left margin: United States. Department of the Interior. Geological Survey. Revisions shown with purple color, compiled by the Geological Survey from aerial photographs taken 1970.
